- Profile Comparison — lock autocomplete fields after selection, Del key to unlock, delete selected rows
- SOQL — query execution can now be cancelled immediately instead of waiting for the current page
- Sharing Settings — Security Type badges and Object Name filter; disk+memory cache per org
- User Roles — progress bar replaces spinner while loading
- User Access Score — clickable Name column opens the permission set directly
- TreeView popup — highlight mode with occurrence counter and up/down navigation
- General — blue/orange/red button styles unified; spinner size increased; icon buttons added
